## Commercial License Exception

Organizations with annual revenue exceeding $1,000,000 USD that wish to use 
Vulpes Celare in ways not permitted by AGPL-3.0 may obtain a commercial license.

Commercial licensing is required for:
- Integration into proprietary/closed-source products
- Offering Vulpes Celare as a managed service without open-sourcing the service
- Using Vulpes Celare in applications where AGPL compliance is not feasible
- Redistributing Vulpes Celare without AGPL obligations

For commercial licensing inquiries, contact: github.com/DocHatty/Vulpes-Celare

