## Compliance

To comply with AGPL-3.0 when using or distributing Vulpes Celare:

1. **If you modify and distribute the software:**
   - Include this LICENSE file
   - Make your source code available
   - License your modifications under AGPL-3.0

2. **If you run it as a network service:**
   - Provide a way for users to download the complete source code
   - Include any modifications you've made
   - This applies even if you don't distribute the software

3. **If you're unsure:**
   - Read the full AGPL-3.0 text at https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html
   - Consult with legal counsel
   - Contact us for clarification or commercial licensing options
